edu.du.penrose.systems.fedoraApp.batchIngest.bus
Class BatchThreadHolder

java.lang.Object
  edu.du.penrose.systems.fedoraApp.batchIngest.bus.BatchThreadHolder
Direct Known Subclasses:
BatchIngestThreadHolder
public abstract class BatchThreadHolder
extends java.lang.Object

Contains a single thread running a specific batch set along with information about the thread and the thread's current status. Among the information stored about the thread is the threads status, the thread's ingest report location and the PID report location. Each thread is an instance of a BatchIngesterController

Author:
chet.rebman
See Also:
BatchIngestThreadManager, FedoraAppBatchIngestController
